#. Tag: title
#: format.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid "Spreadsheet Formatting"
msgstr "Oblikovanje preglednice"

#. Tag: title
#: format.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cell Format"
msgstr "Oblika celice"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To change the format and appearance of selected cell(s), row(s) or column(s) "
"use the <guimenuitem>Cell Format...</guimenuitem> option from the "
"<guimenu>Format</guimenu> menu or from the <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> "
"mouse button popup menu."
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti obliko in videz izbranih celic, vrstic ali stolpcev, "
"uporabite možnost <guimenuitem>Oblika celice...</guimenuitem> v meniju "
"<guimenu>Oblika</guimenu> ali iz pojavni meni <mousebutton>desnega</"
"mousebutton> gumba miške."

#. Tag: phrase
#: format.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid "Right mouse button context menu."
msgstr "Kontekstni meni z desnim gumbom miške."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will bring up the <guilabel>Cell Format</guilabel> dialog box which has "
"several tabbed pages:"
msgstr ""
"To bo prikazalo pogovorno okno <guilabel>Oblika celice</guilabel>, ki ima "
"več strani z zavihki:"

#. Tag: title
#: format.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid "Data Formats and Representation"
msgstr "Podatkovni formati in predstavitev"

#. Tag: phrase
#: format.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Data Format</guilabel> page."
msgstr "Stran <guilabel>Oblika podatkov</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Data Format</guilabel> page of the <guilabel>Cell Format</"
"guilabel> dialog box lets you control how the values of cells are displayed."
msgstr ""
"Stran <guilabel>Oblika podatkov</guilabel> v pogovornem oknu "
"<guilabel>Oblika celice</guilabel> vam omogoča nadzor nad prikazom vrednosti "
"celic."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The top part of this page lets you select the format to be used when "
"displaying numeric values, dates or times. A <guilabel>Preview</guilabel> "
"pane allows you to see the effect of the new format."
msgstr ""
"V zgornjem delu te strani lahko izberete obliko, ki bo uporabljena pri "
"prikazu številskih vrednosti, datumov ali ur. Podokno <guilabel>Predogled</"
"guilabel> vam omogoča, da vidite učinek novega formata."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can set the same data format for a row or a column by selecting the row "
"or column and calling the <guilabel>Cell Format</guilabel> dialog with the "
"&RMB;."
msgstr ""
"Enako obliko podatkov lahko nastavite za vrstico ali stolpec tako, da "
"izberete vrstico ali stolpec in pokličete pogovorno okno <guilabel>Oblika "
"celice</guilabel> z &RMB;."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can increase the precision decimal for any number in <guilabel>Generic</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Number</guilabel>, <guilabel>Percent</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Money</guilabel> or <guilabel>Scientific</guilabel> formats using "
"the <guiicon>Increase precision</guiicon> icon in the <guilabel>Format</"
"guilabel> toolbar:"
msgstr ""
"Natančno decimalko lahko povečate za poljubno število v <guilabel>Generično</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Število</guilabel>, <guilabel>Odstotek</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Denar</guilabel> ali <guilabel>Znanstveno</guilabel> formatira z "
"uporabo ikone <guiicon>Povečaj natančnost</guiicon> v orodni vrstici "
"<guilabel>Oblika</guilabel>:"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can decrease the precision decimal for any number in <guilabel>Generic</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Number</guilabel>, <guilabel>Percent</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Money</guilabel> or <guilabel>Scientific</guilabel> formats using "
"the <guiicon>Decrease precision</guiicon> icon in the <guilabel>Format</"
"guilabel> toolbar:"
msgstr ""
"Decimalno natančnost lahko zmanjšate za poljubno število v "
"<guilabel>Generično</guilabel>, <guilabel>Število</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Odstotek</guilabel>, <guilabel>Denar</guilabel> ali "
"<guilabel>Znanstveno</guilabel> formatira z uporabo ikone <guiicon>Zmanjšaj "
"natančnost</guiicon> v orodni vrstici <guilabel>Oblika</guilabel>:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "Generic"
msgstr "Generično"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the default format and &sheets; autodetects the actual data type "
"depending on the current cell data. By default, &sheets; right justifies "
"numbers, dates and times within a cell and left justifies anything else."
msgstr ""
"To je privzeta oblika in &sheets; samodejno zazna dejanski tip podatkov "
"glede na trenutne podatke celice. Privzeto je &sheets; desno poravna "
"številke, datume in čase v celici, levo pa karkoli drugega."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the <guilabel>Generic</guilabel> format does not suit you, you can change "
"to a specific format among the choices below."
msgstr ""
"Če vam <guilabel>Generično</guilabel> format ne ustreza, lahko med spodnjimi "
"možnostmi spremenite v določen format."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid "Number"
msgstr "Število"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The number notation uses the notation you globally choose in "
"&systemsettings; in <menuchoice><guimenu>Locale</guimenu><guisubmenu>Country/"
"Region &amp; Language</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Numbers</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>. Numbers are right justified by default."
msgstr ""
"Številski zapis uporablja zapis, ki ga globalno izberete v &systemsettings; "
"v <menuchoice><guimenu>Locale</guimenu><guisubmenu>Država/regija &amp; "
"Jezik</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Števila</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Števila "
"so privzeto poravnane desno."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid "Percent"
msgstr "Odstotek"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you have a number in the current cell and you switch the cell format "
"from <guilabel>Generic</guilabel> to <guilabel>Percent</guilabel>, the "
"current cell number will be multiplied by 100."
msgstr ""
"Ko imate v trenutni celici število in preklopite obliko celice iz "
"<guilabel>Generično</guilabel> v <guilabel>Odstotek</guilabel>, bo trenutna "
"številka celice pomnožena s 100."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For example if you enter 2 and set the cell format to <guilabel>Percent</"
"guilabel>, the number will then be 200 %. Switching back to "
"<guilabel>Generic</guilabel> cell format will bring it back to 2."
msgstr ""
"Če na primer vnesete 2 in nastavite obliko celice na <guilabel>Odstotek</"
"guilabel>, bo število 200 %. Če preklopite nazaj na <guilabel>Generično</"
"guilabel> obliko celice, jo boste vrnili na 2."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also use the <guiicon>Percent</guiicon> icon in the "
"<guilabel>Format</guilabel> Toolbar:"
msgstr ""
"Uporabite lahko tudi ikono <guiicon>Odstotek</guiicon> v orodni vrstici "
"<guilabel>Oblika</guilabel>:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid "Money"
msgstr "Denar"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Money</guilabel> format converts your number into money "
"notation using the settings globally fixed in &systemsettings; in "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Locale</guimenu><guisubmenu>Country/Region &amp; "
"Language</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Money</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. The "
"currency symbol will be displayed and the precision will be the one set in "
"&systemsettings;."
msgstr ""
"Format <guilabel>Denar</guilabel> pretvori vaše število v denarni zapis z "
"uporabo nastavitev, ki so globalno določene v &systemsettings; v "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Locale</guimenu><guisubmenu>Država/regija &amp; Jezik</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Denar</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Prikazan bo simbol "
"valute in natančnost bo tista, ki je nastavljena v &systemsettings;."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also use the <guiicon>Money Format</guiicon> icon in the "
"<guilabel>Format</guilabel> toolbar to set the cell formatting to look like "
"your current currency:"
msgstr ""
"Uporabite lahko tudi ikono <guiicon>Oblika denarja</guiicon> v orodni "
"vrstici <guilabel>Oblika</guilabel>, da nastavite oblikovanje celice tako, "
"da bo videti kot vaša trenutna valuta:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scientific"
msgstr "Znanstveno"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Scientific</guilabel> format changes your number using the "
"scientific notation. For example, 0.0012 will be changed to 1.2E-03. Going "
"back using <guilabel>Generic</guilabel> cell format will display 0.0012 "
"again. The <guilabel>Generic</guilabel> cell data format does not keep "
"scientific notation so if you want this notation, you have to specify it "
"using this menu item."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Znanstvena</guilabel> oblika spremeni vaše število z uporabo "
"znanstvenega zapisa. Na primer, 0,0012 bo spremenjeno v 1,2E-03. Če se "
"vrnete nazaj z <guilabel>generičnim</guilabel> formatom celic, bo znova "
"prikazano 0,0012. <guilabel>Generični</guilabel> format podatkov celice ne "
"ohranja znanstvenega zapisa, tako da, če želite ta zapis, ga morate določiti "
"s tem menijskim elementom."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fraction"
msgstr "Ulomek"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Fraction</guilabel> format changes your number into a "
"fraction. For example, 0.1 can be changed to 1/8, 2/16, 1/10, &etc; You "
"define the type of fraction by choosing it in the field on the right. If the "
"exact fraction is not possible in the fraction mode you choose, the nearest "
"closest match is chosen. For example: when we have 1.5 as number, we choose "
"<guilabel>Fraction</guilabel> and <guilabel>Sixteenths 1/16</guilabel> the "
"text displayed into cell is \"1 8/16\" which is an exact fraction. If you "
"have 1.4 as number in your cell and you choose <guilabel>Fraction</guilabel> "
"and <guilabel>Sixteenths 1/16</guilabel> then the cell will display \"1 "
"6/16\" which is the nearest closest Sixteenth fraction."
msgstr ""
"Format <guilabel>Ulomek</guilabel> spremeni vaše število v ulomek. Na "
"primer, 0,1 lahko spremenite v 1/8, 2/16, 1/10 &etc;. Vrsto ulomka določite "
"tako, da jo izberete v polju na desni. Če natančen ulomek ni mogoč v načinu "
"ulomka, ki ga izberete, se izbere najbližje ujemanje. Na primer: ko imamo "
"kot število 1,5, izberemo <guilabel>Ulomek</guilabel> in "
"<guilabel>Šestnajstine 1/16</guilabel>, besedilo, prikazano v celici, je \"1 "
"8/16\", kar je natančen ulomek. Če imate v celici število 1,4 in izberete "
"<guilabel>Ulomek</guilabel> in <guilabel>Šestnajstine 1/16</guilabel>, bo "
"celica prikazala »1 6/16«, ki je skoraj najbližji ulomek šestnajstine ."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid "Date"
msgstr "Datum"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:154
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To enter a date, you should enter it in one of the formats set in "
"&systemsettings; in <menuchoice><guimenu>Locale</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Country/Region &amp; Language</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Date "
"&amp; Time</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. There are two formats set here: the "
"date format and the short date format."
msgstr ""
"Če želite vnesti datum, ga morate vnesti v enem od formatov, nastavljenih v "
"&systemsettings; v <menuchoice><guimenu>Locale</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Država/"
"regija &amp; Jezik</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Datum &amp; Čas</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>. Tu sta nastavljeni dve obliki: oblika datuma in oblika kratkega "
"datuma."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A random natural number NN will be transformed in the date from 30st "
"December 1899 (which is 0) with the number of days NN added. For example if "
"you have a cell with 100 and you choose <guilabel>Date</guilabel> format, "
"\"1900-04-09\" will be displayed in the cell which is 100 days after 30st "
"December 1899. This starting date is two days early as it was a bug in Lotus "
"123 and then it stayed that way in Excel in order to keep compatibility. Few "
"people will need to calculate from 1st January 1900 anyway and adding 9 days "
"to 1st November 2000 for example will give you 10th November 2000 so all "
"normal calculations on dates are correct."
msgstr ""
"Naključno naravno število NN bo pretvorjeno v datum od 30. decembra 1899 (ki "
"je 0) z dodanim številom dni NN. Na primer, če imate celico s 100 in "
"izberete obliko zapisa <guilabel>Datum</guilabel>, bo v celici prikazano "
"\"1900-04-09\", ki je 100 dni po 30. decembru 1899. Ta začetni datum je dva "
"dni prezgodaj je bila napaka v Lotusu 123, nato pa je tako ostalo v Excelu, "
"da bi ohranili združljivost. Nekaj ljudi bo tako ali tako moralo računati od "
"1. januarja 1900 in če na primer 1. novembru 2000 dodate 9 dni, boste dobili "
"10. november 2000, tako da so vsi običajni izračuni datumov pravilni."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:168
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When a cell is in the <guilabel>Date</guilabel> format, you can drag this "
"cell down as you do with numbers and the next cells will also get dates, "
"each date being increased by one day."
msgstr ""
"Ko je celica v formatu <guilabel>Datum</guilabel>, lahko to celico povlečete "
"navzdol, kot to počnete s številkami, in naslednje celice bodo prav tako "
"dobile datume, pri čemer bo vsak datum povečan za en dan."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid "Time"
msgstr "Čas"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This formats your cell content as a time. To enter a time, you should enter "
"it in the <guilabel>Time format</guilabel> set in &systemsettings; in "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Locale</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Country/Region &amp; "
"Language</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Date &amp; Time</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>. In the <guilabel>Cell Format</guilabel> dialog box you can set "
"how the time should be displayed by choosing one of the available time "
"format options. The default format is the system format set in "
"&systemsettings;. When the number in the cell does not make sense as a time, "
"&sheets; will display 00:00 in the global format you have in "
"&systemsettings;."
msgstr ""
"To formatira vsebino vaše celice kot čas. Če želite vnesti čas, ga morate "
"vnesti v <guilabel>Oblika časa</guilabel>, nastavljeno v &systemsettings; v "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Locale</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Država/regija &amp; Jezik</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Datum &amp; Čas</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. V "
"pogovornem oknu <guilabel>Oblika celice</guilabel> lahko nastavite, kako naj "
"bo prikazan čas, tako da izberete eno od razpoložljivih možnosti zapisa "
"časa. Privzeti format je sistemski format, nastavljen v &systemsettings;. Ko "
"številka v celici nima smisla kot čas, &sheets; bo prikazal 00:00 v "
"globalnem formatu, ki ga imate v &systemsettings;."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid "Date and Time"
msgstr "Datum in čas"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This formats your cell content as date and time. To enter a date and a time, "
"you should enter it in the <guilabel>Time format</guilabel> set in "
"&systemsettings; in <menuchoice><guimenu>Locale</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Country/Region &amp; Language</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Date "
"&amp; Time</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. In the <guilabel>Cell Format</"
"guilabel> dialog box you can set how the date and time should be displayed "
"by choosing one of the available date and time format options. The default "
"format is the system format set in &systemsettings;. When the number in the "
"cell does not make sense as a date and time, &sheets; will display 00:00 in "
"the global format you have in &systemsettings;."
msgstr ""
"To formatira vsebino vaše celice kot datum in uro. Če želite vnesti datum in "
"uro, ju morate vnesti v <guilabel>Oblika časa</guilabel>, nastavljeno v "
"&systemsettings; v <menuchoice><guimenu>Locale</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Država/"
"regija &amp; Jezik</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Datum &amp; Čas</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>. V pogovornem oknu <guilabel>Oblika celice</guilabel> lahko "
"nastavite, kako naj bosta prikazana datum in čas, tako da izberete eno od "
"razpoložljivih možnosti zapisa datuma in časa. Privzeti format je sistemski "
"format, nastavljen v &systemsettings;. Ko številka v celici ni smiselna kot "
"datum in čas, &sheets; bo prikazal 00:00 v globalnem formatu, ki ga imate v "
"&systemsettings;."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid "Text"
msgstr "Besedilo"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This formats your cell content as text. This can be useful if you want a "
"number treated as text instead as a number, for example for a ZIP code. "
"Setting a number as text format will left justify it. When numbers are "
"formatted as text, they cannot be used in calculations or formulas. It also "
"change the way the cell is justified."
msgstr ""
"To oblikuje vsebino vaše celice kot besedilo. To je lahko koristno, če "
"želite, da se številka obravnava kot besedilo namesto kot številka, na "
"primer za poštno številko. Če nastavite številko kot obliko besedila, jo "
"poravnate levo. Ko so številke oblikovane kot besedilo, jih ni mogoče "
"uporabiti v izračunih ali formulah. Prav tako spremeni način poravnave "
"celice."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid "Custom"
msgstr "Po meri"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:213
#, no-c-format
msgid "Does not work yet. To be enabled in the next release."
msgstr "Še ne deluje. Omogočeno v naslednji izdaji."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:218
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The lower part of the <guilabel>Data Format</guilabel> page lets you add a "
"<guilabel>Prefix:</guilabel> such as a $ symbol at the start of each item or "
"a <guilabel>Postfix:</guilabel> such as $HK to the end. You can also control "
"how many digits are displayed after the decimal point for numeric values, "
"whether positive values are displayed with a leading + sign and whether "
"negative values are shown in red."
msgstr ""
"Spodnji del strani <guilabel>Oblika podatkov</guilabel> vam omogoča "
"dodajanje <guilabel>Prefix:</guilabel>, kot je simbol $ na začetku vsake "
"postavke ali <guilabel>Postfix:</guilabel> kot je $HK do konca. Prav tako "
"lahko nadzorujete, koliko števk je prikazanih za decimalno vejico za "
"številske vrednosti, ali so pozitivne vrednosti prikazane z začetnim znakom "
"+ in ali so negativne vrednosti prikazane rdeče."

#. Tag: title
#: format.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fonts and Text Settings"
msgstr "Nastavitve pisave in besedila"

#. Tag: phrase
#: format.docbook:235
#, no-c-format
msgid "Font page."
msgstr "Stran s pisavami."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:239
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Font</guilabel> page lets you select the font family, "
"<guilabel>Style:</guilabel>, <guilabel>Size:</guilabel>, <guilabel>Weight:</"
"guilabel> and <guilabel>Color:</guilabel> for the current cell, including "
"some additional options like underlined or striked out text. The lower part "
"of the page gives a <guilabel>Preview</guilabel> of the selected text format."
msgstr ""
"Stran <guilabel>Pisava</guilabel> vam omogoča izbiro družine pisav, "
"<guilabel>Slog:</guilabel>, <guilabel>Velikost:</guilabel>, <guilabel>Teža:</"
"guilabel> in <guilabel> Barva:</guilabel> za trenutno celico, vključno z "
"nekaterimi dodatnimi možnostmi, kot je podčrtano ali prečrtano besedilo. "
"Spodnji del strani ponuja <guilabel>Predogled</guilabel> izbrane oblike "
"besedila."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The default font is set for all cells in the <menuchoice><guimenu>Format</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Style Manager</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu with the "
"currently used style."
msgstr ""
"Privzeta pisava je nastavljena za vse celice v meniju "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Oblika</guimenu><guimenuitem>Upravitelj slogov</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> s trenutno uporabljenim slogom."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:255
#, no-c-format
msgid "Style:"
msgstr "Slog:"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:256
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose the style for your font for the currently selected cells. When you "
"select several cells with different styles, the displayed style is set to "
"<guilabel>Varying (No Change)</guilabel> and leaving it that way will keep "
"all your current style settings for each cell. Changing to <guilabel>Roman</"
"guilabel> for example will change all the selected cells style text to "
"<guilabel>Roman</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Izberite slog pisave za trenutno izbrane celice. Ko izberete več celic z "
"različnimi slogi, je prikazani slog nastavljen na <guilabel>Različen (brez "
"sprememb)</guilabel> in če ga pustite tako, bodo obdržane vse vaše trenutne "
"nastavitve sloga za vsako celico. Če na primer spremenite v <guilabel>Roman</"
"guilabel>, boste spremenili slog besedila vseh izbranih celic v "
"<guilabel>Roman</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:265
#, no-c-format
msgid "Size:"
msgstr "Velikost:"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:266
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose the size for your font for the currently selected cells. When you "
"select several cells with different sizes, the displayed size is set to "
"<guilabel> </guilabel> (no number written) and leaving it that way will keep "
"all your current size settings for each cell. Changing to <guilabel>14</"
"guilabel> for example will change all the selected cells font size to "
"<guilabel>14</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Izberite velikost pisave za trenutno izbrane celice. Ko izberete več celic z "
"različnimi velikostmi, je prikazana velikost nastavljena na <guilabel> </"
"guilabel> (brez zapisane številke) in če jo pustite tako, bodo obdržane vse "
"vaše trenutne nastavitve velikosti za vsako celico. Če na primer spremenite "
"na <guilabel>14</guilabel>, boste spremenili velikost pisave vseh izbranih "
"celic na <guilabel>14</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:275
#, no-c-format
msgid "Weight:"
msgstr "Utež:"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:276
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose the weight for your font for the currently selected cells. When you "
"select several cells with different font weight, the displayed weight is set "
"to <guilabel>Varying (No Change)</guilabel> and leaving it that way will "
"keep all your current weight settings for each cell. Changing to "
"<guilabel>Bold</guilabel> for example will change all the selected cells "
"font weight to <guilabel>Bold</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Izberite težo vaše pisave za trenutno izbrane celice. Ko izberete več celic "
"z različno težo pisave, je prikazana teža nastavljena na "
"<guilabel>Spremenljivo (brez sprememb)</guilabel> in če jo pustite tako, "
"bodo obdržane vse vaše trenutne nastavitve teže za vsako celico. Če na "
"primer spremenite v <guilabel>Krepko</guilabel>, boste spremenili težo "
"pisave vseh izbranih celic v <guilabel>Krepko</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:285
#, no-c-format
msgid "Color:"
msgstr "Barva:"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:286
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose the color for the currently selected cells' text. Clicking on the "
"color bar will bring you the standard KDE <guilabel>Select Color</guilabel> "
"dialog where you will be able to choose the new color."
msgstr ""
"Izberite barvo za besedilo trenutno izbranih celic. S klikom na barvno "
"vrstico se prikaže standardno pogovorno okno KDE <guilabel>Izberite barvo</"
"guilabel>, kjer boste lahko izbrali novo barvo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid "Underline"
msgstr "Podčrtaj"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:293
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Underlines the currently selected cells' text if checked. This is not "
"checked per default."
msgstr ""
"Podčrta besedilo trenutno izbranih celic, če je označeno. To privzeto ni "
"potrjeno."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:299
#, no-c-format
msgid "Strike out"
msgstr "Prečrtano"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will strike out the currently selected cells' text if this is checked. "
"This is not checked per default."
msgstr ""
"To bo prečrtalo besedilo trenutno izbranih celic, če je to označeno. To "
"privzeto ni potrjeno."

#. Tag: title
#: format.docbook:309
#, no-c-format
msgid "Text Position and Rotation"
msgstr "Položaj in vrtenje besedila"

#. Tag: phrase
#: format.docbook:316
#, no-c-format
msgid "Position page."
msgstr "Stran s položajem."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:320
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"From the <guilabel>Position</guilabel> page you can control the position of "
"text within a cell by making suitable selections in the <guilabel>Horizontal "
"</guilabel> and <guilabel>Vertical</guilabel> areas or by setting the "
"<guilabel>Indent</guilabel> value. You can also choose to have the text "
"appear vertically rather than horizontally, or even at an angle."
msgstr ""
"Na strani <guilabel>Položaj</guilabel> lahko nadzirate položaj besedila v "
"celici tako, da naredite ustrezne izbire v območjih <guilabel>Vodoravno </"
"guilabel> in <guilabel>Navpično</guilabel> ali z nastavitvijo "
"<guilabel>Vrednost zamika</guilabel>. Izberete lahko tudi, da se besedilo "
"prikaže navpično namesto vodoravno ali celo pod kotom."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid "Horizontal"
msgstr "Vodoravno"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:329
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the content position horizontally in the cell. <guilabel>Standard</"
"guilabel> is default and is set from the data format you choose. "
"<guilabel>Left</guilabel> means the content will be displayed on the left of "
"the cell. <guilabel>Center</guilabel> means the content will be in the "
"center horizontally in the cell. <guilabel>Right</guilabel> means the "
"content of the cell will be displayed on the right of the cell."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite vodoravni položaj vsebine v celici. <guilabel>Standardno</"
"guilabel> je privzeta in je nastavljena glede na format podatkov, ki ga "
"izberete. <guilabel>Levo</guilabel> pomeni, da bo vsebina prikazana na levi "
"stranicelica. <guilabel>Na sredino</guilabel> pomeni, da bo vsebina na "
"sredini vodoravno v celici. <guilabel>Desno</guilabel> pomeni da bo vsebina "
"celice prikazana na desni strani celice.​"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:338
#, no-c-format
msgid "Vertical"
msgstr "Navpično"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:339
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the content position vertically in the cell. <guilabel>Top</guilabel> "
"means the content will be displayed on top of the cell. <guilabel>Middle</"
"guilabel> means the content will be in the middle vertically in the cell. "
"<guilabel>Bottom</guilabel> means the content of the cell will be displayed "
"at the bottom of the cell."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite položaj vsebine navpično v celici. <guilabel>Na vrhu</guilabel> "
"pomeni, da bo vsebina prikazana na vrhu celice. <guilabel>Sredina</guilabel> "
"pomeni, da bo vsebina v celici navpično na sredini. <guilabel>Dno</guilabel> "
"pomeni, da bo vsebina celice prikazana na dnu celice."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:347
#, no-c-format
msgid "Text Option"
msgstr "Možnost besedila"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:348
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is only available when the rotation is 0°. <guilabel>Wrap text</"
"guilabel> wraps the text so it fits in the previous cell size. If this is "
"not checked, the text will stay on one line."
msgstr ""
"To je na voljo le, če je rotacija 0°. <guilabel>Prelomi besedilo</guilabel> "
"prelomi besedilo tako, da se prilega prejšnji velikosti celice. Če to ni "
"označeno, bo besedilo ostalo v eni vrstici."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:351
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Vertical text</guilabel> puts your text vertically."
msgstr "<guilabel>Navpično besedilo</guilabel> postavi vaše besedilo navpično."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:355
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rotation"
msgstr "Rotacija"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:356
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Your text will appear oriented in the angle you set here. Positive values "
"will move it counter-clockwise and negative values will move it clockwise."
msgstr ""
"Vaše besedilo bo usmerjeno pod kotom, ki ste ga nastavili tukaj. Pozitivne "
"vrednosti ga bodo premaknile v nasprotni smeri urinega kazalca, negativne "
"vrednosti pa v smeri urinega kazalca."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid "Merge Cells"
msgstr "Spoji celice"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:363
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When checked, this has the same effect as <menuchoice><guimenu>Format</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Merge Cells</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. You need to "
"have at least two consecutive cells selected. Those consecutive cells are "
"then merged into a bigger one."
msgstr ""
"Ko je označeno, ima to enak učinek kot <menuchoice><guimenu>Oblika</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Združi celice</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Izbrani "
"morate imeti vsaj dve zaporedni celici. Te zaporedne celice se nato združijo "
"v eno večjo."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:368
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When a merged cell is selected and when you uncheck this, then all cells "
"come back to their original size as before the merging. It has the same "
"effect as <menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu><guimenuitem>Dissociate "
"Cells</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Ko je združena celica izbrana in ko to počistite, se vse celice povrnejo na "
"prvotno velikost kot pred združitvijo. Ima enak učinek kot "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Oblikuj</guimenu><guimenuitem>Razdruži celice</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:375
#, no-c-format
msgid "Indent"
msgstr "Zamik"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:376
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the amount of indent that will be used in the cell when you choose the "
"<guilabel>Increase Indent</guilabel>/<guilabel>Decrease Indent</guilabel> "
"actions from the toolbar. These actions are not enabled by default in the "
"toolbar."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite količino zamika, ki bo uporabljen v celici, ko v orodni vrstici "
"izberete dejanja <guilabel>Povečaj zamik</guilabel>/<guilabel>Zmanjšaj "
"zamik</guilabel>. Ta dejanja v orodni vrstici niso privzeto omogočena."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:382
#, no-c-format
msgid "Size of Cell"
msgstr "Velikost celice"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:383
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You set here the size of the cell, either a custom width and height or "
"choose the default width and height."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj nastavite velikost celice, bodisi širino in višino po meri ali "
"izberete privzeto širino in višino."

#. Tag: title
#: format.docbook:391
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cell Border"
msgstr "Obroba celice"

#. Tag: phrase
#: format.docbook:398
#, no-c-format
msgid "Border page."
msgstr "Stran obrobe."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:402
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Border</guilabel> page lets you set the appearance of the cell "
"borders. If you have selected more than one cell you can apply different "
"styles to the borders between the cells and that surrounding the selected "
"area."
msgstr ""
"Stran <guilabel>Obroba</guilabel> vam omogoča nastavitev videza obrob celic. "
"Če ste izbrali več kot eno celico, lahko uporabite različne sloge za robove "
"med celicami in tiste, ki obkrožajo izbrano območje."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:406
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"First select the pattern and color from the <guilabel>Pattern</guilabel> "
"section of the <guilabel>Border</guilabel> page then apply that to different "
"parts of the border by clicking on the appropriate button in the "
"<guilabel>Border</guilabel> section, or on one of the <guilabel>Preselect </"
"guilabel> buttons. The left hand button in the <guilabel>Preselect </"
"guilabel> section will clear any previously applied border(s). Note that you "
"can also add a diagonal strike-through line to the cell(s)."
msgstr ""
"Najprej izberite vzorec in barvo v razdelku <guilabel>Vzorec</guilabel> na "
"strani <guilabel>Obroba</guilabel>, nato pa to uporabite na različnih delih "
"obrobe s klikom na ustrezen gumb v <guilabel>Obroba</guilabel> ali na enem "
"od gumbov <guilabel>Predizberi </guilabel>. Levi gumb v razdelku "
"<guilabel>Predizberi </guilabel> počisti vse predhodno uporabljene obrobe. "
"Upoštevajte, da lahko v celico(e) dodate tudi diagonalno prečrtano črto."

#. Tag: title
#: format.docbook:415
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cell Background"
msgstr "Ozadje celice"

#. Tag: phrase
#: format.docbook:422
#, no-c-format
msgid "Background page."
msgstr "Stran ozadja."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:426
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The cell background pattern and color can be selected from the "
"<guilabel>Background</guilabel> page."
msgstr ""
"Vzorec in barvo ozadja celice lahko izberete na strani <guilabel>Ozadje</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:428
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Simply choose a desired <guilabel>Pattern</guilabel>, then select the "
"pattern <guilabel>Color</guilabel> and the <guilabel>Background color</"
"guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Preprosto izberite želeni <guilabel>vzorec</guilabel>, nato izberite vzorec "
"<guilabel>barvo</guilabel> in <guilabel>barvo ozadja</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:430
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At the bottom of this page you can see a <guilabel>Preview</guilabel> of the "
"configured cell background."
msgstr ""
"Na dnu te strani lahko vidite <guilabel>Predogled</guilabel> konfiguriranega "
"ozadja celice."

#. Tag: title
#: format.docbook:434
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cell Protection"
msgstr "Zaščita celic"

#. Tag: phrase
#: format.docbook:441
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cell protection page."
msgstr "Stran za zaščito celic."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:445
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can change the way the content of a cell is protected in the "
"<guilabel>Cell Protection</guilabel> page."
msgstr ""
"Način zaščite vsebine celice lahko spremenite na strani <guilabel>Zaščita "
"celice</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:447
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All cells are protected by default (that means cell content cannot be "
"changed) and for the cell protection to be active you also need to protect "
"the sheet using the <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Protect "
"Sheet...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu and to provide a password. You can "
"also hide the cell formula in order to protect the way you calculate the "
"formula. This also needs to enable sheet protection to work. You can hide "
"the cell content with <guilabel>Hide all</guilabel> and again this needs "
"sheet protection. You can learn more about all these settings in the <link "
"linkend=\"protection\">Advanced &sheets; chapter, Protection section</link>."
msgstr ""
"Vse celice so privzeto zaščitene (kar pomeni, da vsebine celice ni mogoče "
"spremeniti) in da je zaščita celice aktivna, morate zaščititi tudi list z "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Zaščiti list. .</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> in za vnos gesla. Formulo celice lahko tudi "
"skrijete, da zaščitite način izračuna formule. To mora tudi omogočiti "
"delovanje zaščite listov. Vsebino celice lahko skrijete z <guilabel>Skrij "
"vse</guilabel> in spet potrebuje zaščito lista. Več o vseh teh nastavitvah "
"lahko izveste v <link linkend=\"protection\">Napredni &sheets; poglavje, "
"razdelek Zaščita</link>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:460
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hide all"
msgstr "Skrij vse"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:461
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This hides the cell content and works only when the sheet is protected which "
"means that changing the <guilabel>Hide all</guilabel> attribute of a cell "
"has no effect unless the sheet is protected. Whether the cell itself is "
"protected or not does not matter."
msgstr ""
"To skrije vsebino celice in deluje le, če je list zaščiten, kar pomeni, da "
"sprememba atributa <guilabel>Skrij vse</guilabel> celice nima učinka, razen "
"če je list zaščiten. Ni pomembno, ali je celica sama zaščitena ali ne."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:465
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When <guilabel>Hide all</guilabel> is selected, <guilabel>Protected</"
"guilabel> and <guilabel>Hide formula</guilabel> are disabled as when the "
"sheet is protected <guilabel>Hide all</guilabel> hides the cell content and "
"the formula and thus masks and protects the cell content."
msgstr ""
"Ko je izbrana možnost <guilabel>Skrij vse</guilabel>, sta "
"<guilabel>Zaščiteno</guilabel> in <guilabel>Skrij formulo</guilabel> "
"onemogočeni, ko je list zaščiten, <guilabel>Skrij vse</guilabel> skrije "
"vsebino celice in formulo ter tako prikrije in zaščiti vsebino celice."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:472
#, no-c-format
msgid "Protected"
msgstr "Zaščiteno"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:473
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If checked, the cell content will be protected. This is the default "
"behaviour. You need to protect the whole sheet using the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Protect Sheet...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu for this individual cell protection to work. "
"When a cell is protected, its content cannot be changed."
msgstr ""
"Če je označeno, bo vsebina celice zaščitena. To je privzeto vedenje. Celoten "
"list morate zaščititi z menijem <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Zaščiti list...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, da bo ta "
"zaščita posamezne celice delovala. Ko je celica zaščitena, njene vsebine ni "
"mogoče spreminjati."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:481
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hide formula"
msgstr "Skrij formulo"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:482
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When this is checked, the cell is still visible. However, its contents do "
"not appear in the <guilabel>Formula</guilabel> bar. Hiding formula is only "
"working for cells that contain formulae so the user cannot view the formula. "
"And the sheet must be protected for this to work."
msgstr ""
"Ko je to označeno, je celica še vedno vidna. Vendar se njegova vsebina ne "
"pojavi v vrstici <guilabel>Formula</guilabel>. Skrivanje formule deluje samo "
"za celice, ki vsebujejo formule, tako da si uporabnik ne more ogledati "
"formule. In list mora biti zaščiten, da to deluje."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:490
#, no-c-format
msgid "Do not print text"
msgstr "Ne natisni besedila"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:491
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you check <guilabel>Do not print text</guilabel> then the text in the "
"cell will not be printed. This is unchecked per default which means that the "
"cell text will always be printed by default."
msgstr ""
"Če označite <guilabel>Ne natisni besedila</guilabel>, bo besedilo vcelica ne "
"bo natisnjena. To privzeto ni potrjeno, kar pomeni, da bo besedilo celice "
"vedno privzeto natisnjeno."

#. Tag: title
#: format.docbook:501
#, no-c-format
msgid "Conditional Cell Attributes"
msgstr "Pogojni atributi celice"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:502
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can make the appearance of a cell change according to the value it "
"contains, useful perhaps if you are using &sheets; to keep track of your "
"household expenses and want to highlight any item greater than, say, one "
"thousand dollars."
msgstr ""
"Videz celice lahko spremenite glede na vrednost, ki jo vsebuje, kar je morda "
"uporabno, če uporabljate &sheets; da spremljate svoje gospodinjske izdatke "
"in želite izpostaviti vsako postavko, ki je večja od, na primer, tisoč "
"dolarjev."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:506
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To do this select the cell(s) then choose <guimenuitem>Conditional Styles..."
"</guimenuitem> from the <guimenu>Format</guimenu> menu. This will bring up "
"the <guilabel>Conditional Styles</guilabel> dialog box where you can make "
"the font type and color of a cell change when the value meets one or more "
"conditions. Note that the second and third conditions only apply if the "
"previous condition(s) are not met."
msgstr ""
"Če želite to narediti, izberite celico(e) in nato izberite "
"<guimenuitem>Pogojni slogi...</guimenuitem> v meniju <guimenu>Oblika</"
"guimenu>. S tem se prikaže pogovorno okno <guilabel>Pogojni slogi</"
"guilabel>, kjer lahko spremenite vrsto pisave in barvo celice, ko vrednost "
"izpolnjuje enega ali več pogojev. Upoštevajte, da drugi in tretji pogoj "
"veljata le, če prejšnji pogoj(-i) niso izpolnjeni."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:512
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <menuchoice><guisubmenu>Clear</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Conditional "
"Styles</guimenuitem></menuchoice> from the <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> menu to "
"clear any conditional attributes from selected cells."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite <menuchoice><guisubmenu>Počisti</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>pogojne "
"sloge</guimenuitem></menuchoice> iz menija <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu>, da "
"počistite vse pogojne atribute iz izbranih celic."

#. Tag: title
#: format.docbook:518
#, no-c-format
msgid "Changing Cell Sizes"
msgstr "Spreminjanje velikosti celic"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:519
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Position</guilabel> page in the <guilabel>Cell Format</"
"guilabel> dialog lets you alter the size of the selected cell(s). Note that "
"changing the height of a single cell will change the height for all cells in "
"that row, similarly changing the width will affect the entire column."
msgstr ""
"Stran <guilabel>Položaj</guilabel> v pogovornem oknu <guilabel>Oblika "
"celice</guilabel> vam omogoča spreminjanje velikosti izbranih celic. "
"Upoštevajte, da bo sprememba višine posamezne celice spremenila višino vseh "
"celic v tej vrstici, podobno bo sprememba širine vplivala na celoten stolpec."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:523
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also select the row(s) or column(s) to be changed then select "
"<guimenuitem>Resize Row...</guimenuitem> or <guimenuitem>Resize Column...</"
"guimenuitem> from the <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> mouse button pop up "
"menu or from the <menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu><guisubmenu>Row</"
"guisubmenu> </menuchoice> or <menuchoice><guimenu>Format</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu> Column</guisubmenu></menuchoice> menu."
msgstr ""
"Izberete lahko tudi vrstice ali stolpce, ki jih želite spremeniti, nato "
"izberite <guimenuitem>Spremeni velikost vrstice...</guimenuitem> ali "
"<guimenuitem>Spremeni velikost stolpca...</guimenuitem> z <mousebutton>desne "
"</mousebutton> pojavni meni gumba miške ali iz <menuchoice><guimenu>Oblika</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Vrstica</guisubmenu> </menuchoice> ali "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Oblika</guimenu><guisubmenu> Stolpec</guisubmenu></"
"menuchoice> menija."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:529
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you move the mouse cursor so that its tip is over the line between two of "
"the row numbers at the left of &sheets;'s window the cursor will change to "
"show two parallel lines each with a short arrow headed line coming from it. "
"When the cursor is in this state you can hold the <mousebutton>left </"
"mousebutton> mouse button down and drag the border between the two rows, "
"changing the height of the upper row. A similar technique can be used to "
"change the width of a column."
msgstr ""
"Če kazalec miške premaknete tako, da je njegova konica nad črto med dvema "
"številkama vrstic na levi strani okna &sheets;, se bo kazalec spremenil "
"tako, da bo prikazal dve vzporedni črti, vsaka s kratko črto s puščico, ki "
"prihaja iz nje. Ko je kazalec v tem stanju, lahko držite pritisnjen "
"<mousebutton>levi </mousebutton> gumb miške in povlečete mejo med obema "
"vrsticama, pri čemer spremenite višino zgornje vrstice. Podobno tehniko "
"lahko uporabite za spreminjanje širine stolpca."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:537
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To set the row height or column width to the minimum needed to display the "
"contents, select the whole row or column, and click with the &RMB; on the "
"row or column label. In the menu which appears, select <guimenuitem>Adjust "
"Row</guimenuitem> or <guimenuitem>Adjust Column</guimenuitem>. The row or "
"column will resize to the minimum necessary. You can also select a single "
"cell or range of cells, and click <guimenuitem>Adjust Row &amp; Column</"
"guimenuitem> from either the &RMB; popup menu or the <guimenu>Format</"
"guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"Če želite nastaviti višino vrstice ali širino stolpca na minimum, potreben "
"za prikaz vsebine, izberite celotno vrstico ali stolpec in kliknite z &RMB; "
"na oznaki vrstice ali stolpca. V meniju, ki se prikaže, izberite "
"<guimenuitem>Prilagodi vrstico</guimenuitem> ali <guimenuitem>Prilagodi "
"stolpec</guimenuitem>. Velikost vrstice ali stolpca se bo spremenila na "
"najmanjšo potrebno. Izberete lahko tudi eno celico ali obseg celic in "
"kliknete <guimenuitem>Prilagodi vrstico &amp; Stolpec</guimenuitem> iz &RMB; "
"pojavni meni ali meni <guimenu>Oblika</guimenu>."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:546
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can make a number of adjacent rows or columns the same size by selecting "
"them then choosing <menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu><guisubmenu> Row</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Equalize Row</guimenuitem></menuchoice> or "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu><guisubmenu>Column</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Equalize Column</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Več sosednjih vrstic ali stolpcev lahko naredite enake velikosti, tako da "
"jih izberete in nato izberete <menuchoice><guimenu>Oblika</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu> Vrstica</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Izravnaj vrstico</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali <menuchoice><guimenu>Oblika</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Stolpec</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Izravnaj stolpec</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: format.docbook:555
#, no-c-format
msgid "Merging Cells"
msgstr "Spajanje celic"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:556
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is often convenient to have one cell that spreads across two or more "
"columns or down more than one row. This can be done by merging two or more "
"cells into one. Select the cells to be merged than choose "
"<menuchoice><guimenu> Format</guimenu><guimenuitem>Merge Cells</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Pogosto je priročno imeti eno celico, ki se razteza čez dva ali več stolpcev "
"ali navzdol v več kot eno vrstico. To lahko storite z združitvijo dveh ali "
"več celic v eno. Izberite celice, ki jih želite spojiti, nato pa izberite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu> Oblika</guimenu><guimenuitem>Združi celice</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:560
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To reverse this process, select the merged cell then choose <guimenuitem> "
"Dissociate Cells</guimenuitem> from the <guimenu>Format</guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"Če želite obrniti ta postopek, izberite združeno celico in nato izberite "
"<guimenuitem> Razdruži celice</guimenuitem> v meniju <guimenu>Oblika</"
"guimenu>."

#. Tag: title
#: format.docbook:565
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hiding Rows and Columns"
msgstr "Skrivanje vrstic in stolpcev"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:566
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A finished spreadsheet can often be made to look more attractive by hiding "
"the cells containing intermediate calculations so that only the important "
"data input and result areas are shown."
msgstr ""
"Dokončano preglednico lahko pogosto naredite bolj privlačno tako, da "
"skrijete celice, ki vsebujejo vmesne izračune, tako da so prikazana le "
"pomembna področja vnosa podatkov in rezultatov."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:569
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In &sheets; you can hide selected rows or columns by using the "
"<guimenuitem>Hide Rows</guimenuitem> and <guimenuitem>Hide Columns</"
"guimenuitem> options from the <menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Row</guisubmenu></menuchoice>, <menuchoice><guimenu>Format </"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Column</guisubmenu></menuchoice> or <mousebutton>right</"
"mousebutton> mouse button menus. Hidden rows and columns are not displayed "
"on the screen or included in a print out."
msgstr ""
"V &sheets; lahko skrijete izbrane vrstice ali stolpce z uporabo možnosti "
"<guimenuitem>Skrij vrstice</guimenuitem> in <guimenuitem>Skrij stolpce</"
"guimenuitem> v <menuchoice><guimenu>Oblika</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Vrstica</"
"guisubmenu ></menuchoice>, <menuchoice><guimenu>Oblika </"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Stolpec</guisubmenu></menuchoice> ali "
"<mousebutton>desni</mousebutton> meniji miškinega gumba. Skrite vrstice in "
"stolpci niso prikazani na zaslonu ali vključeni v izpis."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:576
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Hiding cells in this way also makes them slightly less prone to accidental "
"change."
msgstr ""
"Skrivanje celic na ta način tudi naredi nekoliko manj nagnjene k naključnim "
"spremembam."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:578
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To un-hide a row or column select <menuchoice><guisubmenu>Row </"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Show Rows...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> or "
"<menuchoice><guisubmenu>Column</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Show Columns...</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> from the <guimenu>Format</guimenu> menu. In the "
"dialog box which appears, you can select any number of rows to show."
msgstr ""
"Če želite odkriti vrstico ali stolpec, izberite "
"<menuchoice><guisubmenu>Vrstica </guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Pokaži vrstice...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali <menuchoice><guisubmenu>Stolpec</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem >Pokaži stolpce ...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> iz "
"menija <guimenu>Oblika</guimenu>. V pogovornem oknu, ki se prikaže, lahko "
"izberete poljubno število vrstic za prikaz."

#. Tag: title
#: format.docbook:587
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sheet properties"
msgstr "Lastnosti lista"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:588
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can access the current sheet properties either by right clicking on the "
"sheet tab and choosing <guilabel>Sheet Properties</guilabel> or by using the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Sheet</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Sheet Properties</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu. "
"Please note that you can only access the <guilabel>Sheet Properties</"
"guilabel> when the document or the sheet is not protected."
msgstr ""
"Do trenutnih lastnosti lista lahko dostopate bodisi z desnim klikom na "
"zavihek lista in izbiro <guilabel>Lastnosti lista</guilabel> ali z uporabo "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Oblika</guimenu> <guisubmenu>List</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Lastnosti lista</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. "
"Upoštevajte, da lahko do <guilabel>Lastnosti lista</guilabel> dostopate le, "
"če dokument ali list nista zaščitena."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:595
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can set different properties that will be valid in the current sheet. "
"Clicking on <guibutton>OK</guibutton> will validate your changes and "
"<guibutton>Defaults</guibutton> will bring back the default settings."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite lahko različne lastnosti, ki bodo veljavne na trenutnem listu. S "
"klikom na <guibutton>V redu</guibutton> bodo vaše spremembe potrjene in "
"<guibutton>Privzete</guibutton> povrne privzete nastavitve."

#. Tag: phrase
#: format.docbook:604
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sheet Properties dialog."
msgstr "Pogovorno okno Lastnosti lista."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:610
#, no-c-format
msgid "Layout direction:"
msgstr "Smer postavitve:"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:611
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Let you choose the sheet orientation. Default is that the first column of "
"the sheet is on the left. If you choose <guilabel>Right to Left</guilabel>, "
"then the first column will be on the right and the others added from right "
"to left."
msgstr ""
"Dovolite, da izberete orientacijo lista. Privzeto je, da je prvi stolpec "
"lista na levi strani. Če izberete <guilabel>Od desne proti levi</guilabel>, "
"bo prvi stolpec na desni, ostali pa dodani od desne proti levi."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:617
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hide zero"
msgstr "Skrij ničlo"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:618
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this box is checked any cell containing the value zero will appear blank."
msgstr ""
"Če je to polje potrjeno, bodo vse celice, ki vsebujejo vrednost nič, prazne."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:623
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatic recalculation"
msgstr "Samodejni preračun"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:624
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This setting controls whether formulae are recalculated automatically when "
"the value of any cell they refer to changes."
msgstr ""
"Ta nastavitev nadzira, ali se formule samodejno znova izračunajo, ko se "
"spremeni vrednost katere koli celice, na katero se nanašajo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:629
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show column as numbers"
msgstr "Pokaži stolpec kot številke"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:630
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this box is checked the column headings will show as numbers rather than "
"as letters. Letters are default."
msgstr ""
"Če je to polje označeno, bodo naslovi stolpcev prikazani kot številke in ne "
"kot črke. Privzete so črke."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:635
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use LC mode"
msgstr "Uporabite način LC"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:636
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this box is checked the cell reference shown at the left end of the "
"Formula Bar will be displayed in LC mode (i.e. L2C3) rather than in its "
"normal form B3. This does not seem to be of much use at the moment."
msgstr ""
"Če je to polje potrjeno, bo referenca celice, prikazana na levem koncu "
"vrstice formule, prikazana v načinu LC (tj. L2C3) in ne v običajni obliki "
"B3. Zdi se, da to trenutno ni prav koristno."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:642
#, no-c-format
msgid "Convert first letter to uppercase"
msgstr "Pretvori prvo črko v veliko"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:643
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check this box and the first letter of any text you type in will "
"automatically be converted to uppercase."
msgstr ""
"Označite to polje in prva črka besedila, ki ga vnesete, bo samodejno "
"pretvorjena v velike črke."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:648
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show grid"
msgstr "Pokaži mrežo"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:649
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If checked the grid (the cell limits) will be shown. This is default. If you "
"uncheck it, the grid will be hidden."
msgstr ""
"Če je označeno, bo prikazana mreža (meje celic). To je privzeto. Če "
"počistite to polje, bo mreža skrita."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:654
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show page borders"
msgstr "Pokaži obrobe strani"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:655
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you check this option, the page borders will be drawn on your current "
"sheet. Per default the page borders are not displayed. It is useful to see "
"the page borders if you want to print your sheet."
msgstr ""
"Če označite to možnost, bodo obrobe strani narisane na vašem trenutnem "
"listu. Obrobe strani privzeto niso prikazane. Koristno je videti obrobe "
"strani, če želite natisniti svoj list."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:661
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show formula"
msgstr "Prikaži formulo"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:662
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this box is checked &sheets; will display the actual formulae in cells "
"rather than the results."
msgstr ""
"Če je to polje potrjeno &sheets; bo prikazal dejanske formule v celicah in "
"ne rezultatov."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:667
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show formula indicator"
msgstr "Pokaži indikator formule"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:668
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this box is checked &sheets; will display a small blue triangle at the "
"bottom left corner of cells containing formulae. This is useful if you want "
"to protect cells with formulae."
msgstr ""
"Če je to polje potrjeno &sheets; bo prikazal majhen modri trikotnik v "
"spodnjem levem kotu celic, ki vsebujejo formule. To je uporabno, če želite "
"zaščititi celice s formulami."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:674
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show comment indicator"
msgstr "Pokaži indikator komentarja"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:675
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this box is checked cells containing comments will be marked by a small "
"red triangle at the top right corner."
msgstr ""
"Če je to polje označeno, bodo celice s komentarji označene z majhnim rdečim "
"trikotnikom v zgornjem desnem kotu."
